---
description: React/TSX (and JSX) UI patterns for the frontend
globs:
  - "frontend/**/*.tsx"
  - "frontend/**/*.jsx"
alwaysApply: false
---

# UI components

- Functional components only; no class components.
- Prefer colocated hooks in the same file or a sibling module next to the component (match how `CustomHooks/` and existing containers do it).

# Types

- Avoid `any`. If types are unknown, use `unknown` and narrow.

# Imports

- Match the existing import style in the file you edit (path vs relative).
